Name: SourceClassificationItemReference
Description: The source item refers to the Classification Item in the source Statistical Classification. TypeOfObject should be set to ClassificationItem.

Name: TargetClassificationItemReference
Description: The target item refers to the Classification Item in the target Statistical Classification. TypeOfObject should be set to ClassificationItem.

Name: IsComplete
Description: Specifies whether the relationship between the two Classification Items is partial or complete.

Name: ValidFrom
Description: Date from which the Map became valid. The date must be defined if the Map belongs to a floating Correspondence Table.

Name: ValidTo
Description: Date at which the Map became invalid. The date must be defined if the Map belongs to a floating Correspondence Table and is no longer valid.
